,"msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>關你撚事 咁叻自己搭的士<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n堅臭，你好鐘意嗅？</blockquote><br />\n喺人出汗耐咗都會有陣味你老豆老母你姑媽姑姐家姐姐夫你自己都喺，覺得自己臭可以縮返你老母條閪。"},{"pid":"80ce8f9d3b16075fcbf27b83daa998a85796691f","tid":384433,"uid":27664,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T10:36:16.000Z","msg":"煙味再加身臭味加落雨濕味 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a5d1710ff7a996290f5650777d885b485c41c42","tid":384433,"uid":30495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T10:36:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>煙味再加身臭味加落雨濕味 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n落雨做野比你又捱唔捱到啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69e8516677692e690758a7849e259d05d42504eb","tid":384433,"uid":88228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T10:58:36.000Z","msg":"地盤佬經過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  sorry 一定香過你"},{"pid":"79728ffc4bce9a03f5282935b41d8a02e962b0b1","tid":384433,"uid":123833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T10:59:14.000Z","msg":"屌你老母得罪你咩"},{"pid":"13314544dcc0e70cf4181b783dae9e3562658721","tid":384433,"uid":100760,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T11:03:57.000Z","msg":"樓主咁高尚都要同地盤佬一齊搭巴士？"},{"pid":"a3ef4966a12942045229437928afb11abde163bf","tid":384433,"uid":128953,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T11:09:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主咁高尚都要同地盤佬一齊搭巴士？</blockquote><br />\n樓豬自覺高尚，咪一樣係地盤佬起既樓到住既賤民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bb03706c3212a7c64404fc10ecd99e077548c2a","tid":384433,"uid":137395,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T12:11:02.000Z","msg":"你夠膽咪當面同距講囉，睇距打唔打柒你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n   <br />\n<br />\n利申:地盤佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32dad69d1e3fff2b79dfad3eb2258ab290ede48e","tid":384433,"uid":22575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T12:12:41.000Z","msg":"有錢搭直升機岀入囉on 仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22db60975bb2e2525c398735bbbfd1c51094b56b","tid":384433,"uid":5809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T12:35:46.000Z","msg":"老實講，如果班師傅做完成日野，但唔抺身就走人真係好撚臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同佢地一齊做野冇所謂，但放工抺身唔駛5分鐘，班師傅都懶，仲要同佢地一齊迫地鐵真係好難頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：全職地盤佬，日日都要上樓面曬太陽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a125b81ce6387cafc76709043bed8579d85b84d","tid":384433,"uid":6058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T15:25:40.000Z","msg":"九成地盤佬都會抹身<br />\n我見過有泥水佬/釘板佬帶埋沫浴露<br />\n個水喉位一到4點開始就會好香<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n反而我返OFFICE時<br />\n見到班西裝佬成身大汗<br />\n但要著住套老西冇得除<br />\n又抹唔到汗<br />\n行過佢哋身邊臭撚過我打完波返來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79004469299527ae238f6f36af0795e94befcfb5","tid":384433,"uid":136662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T15:48:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>九成地盤佬都會抹身<br />\n我見過有泥水佬/釘板佬帶埋沫浴露<br />\n個水喉位一到4點開始就會好香<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n反而我返OFFICE時<br />\n見到班西裝佬成身大汗<br />\n但要著住套老西冇得除<br />\n又抹唔到汗<br />\n行過佢哋身邊臭撚過我打完波返來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌以前未做野都係諗地盤佬唔整潔<br />\n仆街依家係西做<br />\nd師父句句唔該 又會帶定多件衫放工沖涼換<br />\n無咩特別野都幾客氣"},{"pid":"21056503f170f75f461e8df2cb2858213b51af97","tid":384433,"uid":6058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T16:08:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>九成地盤佬都會抹身<br />\n我見過有泥水佬/釘板佬帶埋沫浴露<br />\n個水喉位一到4點開始就會好香<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n反而我返OFFICE時<br />\n見到班西裝佬成身大汗<br />\n但要著住套老西冇得除<br />\n又抹唔到汗<br />\n行過佢哋身邊臭撚過我打完波返來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌以前未做野都係諗地盤佬唔整潔<br />\n仆街依家係西做<br />\nd師父句句唔該 又會帶定多件衫放工沖涼換<br />\n無咩特別野都幾客氣</blockquote><br />\n其實偏見呢家嘢<br />\n真係好難改<br />\n尤其是社會上嘅偏見<br />\n就好似愛滋咁<br />\n就算知道日常社交唔會傳染<br />\n但啲人都係會有偏見<br />\n不過無知就唔好表現出來<br />\n睇下人哋點講先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}